{"word":"ἀναπαυστήριος","slug":"ἀναπαυστήριος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναπαυστήριος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀναπαύω'><el>ἀναπαύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>of</i> or <i>for resting</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a> <el>ἀναπαυστήριον, τό</el>, <i>a time of rest</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a place of rest</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}